social_posts.post_text: We had the pleasure of attending as one of my best friends, @amshaiken, twin girls, @korie.shaiken & @elexa_shaiken were called to the Torah as a B’Not Mitzvah. Korie & Elexa, you were incredible. I was sweating watching you both up there commanding the stage.  @jshaiken did amazing big-sistering throughout. It’s been amazing watching you both grow up. I know Dad & mom, @lshaiken , are so proud. Thanks for having us be part of your big day. It was, indeed, BUSSIN ❤️

Ep 5 of @dcdoompatrol is streaming now on @hbomax ! @shoshanasachi  wrote an incredible episode. I had a blast working with @matthew.zuk & my old pal @mattbomer . A little BTS goodness for you. Finale of part 1 of season 4 is next week! Make sure ur caught up 😊

HE’S BAAAAAACK! Honored to come back as Bloodwork in the final season of @cwtheflash ! It’s gonna blow ur mind. Congrats to the entire cast and crew on a historic 9 season run. Never had so much fun being so evil 😈. @tvline @warnerbrostv
The South Asian Excellence At The Oscars event was last night. Most excellent was meeting @malala . What an honor.
This portrait is entitled: SOME GUY AND TWO STUNNERS
All caught up on #TheFlash? You just might see a familiar face soon 😈
So proud to be a part of this film. Congrats to the entire #secretartofhumanflight team on being selected for @tribecafilmfestival !! See you all soon! #tribecafilmfestival2023

Hope you all enjoyed last nights ep of @cwtheflash ! The episode was massive & @dpanabaker did an amazing job. I want to thank #EricWallace & the entire cast & crew for having me back. Also a huge thank you to @davidrapaport for making this all happen for me. To the fans, it’s been an honor being ur #Bloodwork. Enjoy the last few eps of the series. See you down the road sometime soon ❤️

I stand with all my writer friends. They deserve a new contract that takes into account the changing landscape of tv & film and their huge contribution to the studios record profits. The WGAs asks are not greedy or unreasonable. Fair is fair 💪🏾

Happy @neverhaveiever day! The 4th and final season is out now and streaming on @netflix worldwide 🌍 I’m posting an old pic cuz all the pics I have of season 4 are slightly spoiler-y so…I’M GIVING YOU 24 hours to binge THE WHOLE SEASON b4 I post all my BTS pics 2moro. Got a job? No problem, call in sick, u deserve a day off. Actually sick? Perfect, now you have something to cheer you up. Basically what I’m saying is, NO EXCUSES. GET TO BINGING! There is so much to say about what being part of this show has meant to me. This cast has my heart ❤️. I have popped in and out of the show for 4 seasons and they have ALWAYS made me feel right at home every time I’m on set. Thank you to all of you. You’re such a hugely talented bunch and I can’t wait to see what you all get up to next. @mindykaling , @loulielang , thank you for having me along for the ride. It’s been such an honor being your Mohan. I have no idea why you chose me but I am forever grateful. To be a small part of South Asian representation on tv has been one of the proudest moments of my career. That representation is only getting started and it is due in no small part, to Mindy, Lang, and all the other talented WRITERS WHO CREATE STORIES THAT CHANGE THE STATUS QUO #PAYTHEM #WGASTRONG . To the fans, all I can do express gratitude for all the love you have given this show and dear, departed, Mohan. We would be nothing without you guys and I thank you from the bottom of my ❤️. See you on the next one! Xx
K. So…all new appreciation post 🤦🏾‍♂️🤦🏾‍♂️🤦🏾‍♂️. Thank you @neverhaveiever fans for all ur support and love over the seasons. You guys have meant the world to us. Best fandom EVA ❤️

@humanflightfilm premiered at @tribeca last night! I hadn’t seen the film yet so went in with no expectation. I LOVE THIS FILM. @hpmendoza has made a beautiful, touching, funny film about the process of grieving the loss of a loved one and I really hope you all get to see it. If you are in NYC, there is a screening today and another one on Tuesday. You won’t regret it. Hopefully a distributor has the good sense to pick this film up so everyone can see @grantrosenmeyer @racipaul @maggiegrace and the rest of this tremendously talented cast I got to be part of shine. @tina_carbone_films @hollywoodhindu
Congrats @neverhaveiever fam on being THE #1 SHOW ON @NETFLIX GLOBALLY !!!!! ❤️💪🏾

Had the pleasure of attending The New York Diwali Gala in support of The Asian-American Writers’ Workshop. Great people, great food, great music. Happy (early) Diwali everyone!
